reviews.text: Great views from my room. Smelled a little musty though. Bathroom was a little dated. Loved that they provided toiletries (toothbrush, razor). Didn’t quite like the carpet flooring because it was hard to roll luggage to my room. Concierge was very helpful with moving my luggage around (they have a storage room if you need to leave luggage there after check out). Location is good if want to stay in the shopping district. Its about 15 minutes to walk to TST - where my wife and I spent most of our time. They also have taxi service is downstairs.

I love staying at the Royal Pacific Hotel. It's located in the shopping district of Kowloon along Canton Street and everything is so accessible.  The malls are just a short walk away. Restaurants are everywhere, too. It has an amazing view of the harbor while a park is just across it. A taxi ramp is nearby or  you go by train as the train station is within walking distance. Rooms are spacious and clean with amazing view. Hotel crews are helpful and knows English. A place to stay while in Hongkong.

Excellent place to stay, young or old, nice property connected to a mall and the harbor. Hotel room was modern feeling and very clean and secure. Stayed in a corner harbor view room ( felt like full harbor view, worth it!) was able to take nice city harbor view picks from the room window, room was bigger than i expected.  Decent exercise room. Staff was very friendly, they assist with bags as well. Perfect location and accessibility to main roads. Main Train station 7 min walk, park 5 min walk(has flamingos and other cool birds, thought i heard a monkey too), shopping 1 min walk ( connected to mall), grocery pantry downstairs next to McDonald's, pier 1 min walk (directly outside, stunning city views at night). Airport 20 min by cab ( woke up late), train is about 25 mins but waaaay cheaper than cab, 15 min by train to ocean park ( cool coaster rides, live Panda.   Shhhhh!).
Absolutely excellent hotel (I'm still here!). Big clean rooms, very helpful staff and amazing Canton Rd location. The breakfast and kitchen are first class.
Excellent hotel!!!    Very good location and absolutely amazing customer services!

reviews.text: Tasty Hainan Chicken good service

Ordered Hoi Nam Chicken rice and Satay. Both were very good. Just a little pricy. 
The ambient is nice. Not crowded and very comfortable.
Food still ok and Hoi Nam Chicken is expensive.  It is now seldom full even Friday evening.

Ordered a Laksah, Nasi Goreng... which were delicious!!! I tried the chensol, and made the mistake of not mixing it first. Beware!! It's really sweet :) otherwise, enjoy! Great place to lunch before leaving to Macau!
Hit and miss with some of the dishes, serious over use of fish sauce which can be off-putting. However the laksa is brilliant

to graduation dinner 搞手:
別看google說要從柯士甸站走路過嚟要十分鐘很嚇人， 其實只是係F出口穿過隧道見到戲曲中心再行前少少就係， 喺中港城入面嘅。
要數這裏的優點很多， 首先職員破例地讓我們早半小時到場set up， 而且全程也有足夠的職員人手在旁協助。 他們都很友善親切以及細心， 會主動斟熱水畀兩位mc非常體貼。 這一點我是非常意外而感到窩心的。 場地方面雖然 在地面那層進來的確 矮矮 的樓底嚇到了。 但職員非常細心地引令到我們的謝師宴場地。 至於食物方面， 選擇應有盡有而且refill也很快， 有湯有包有cold cut有壽司有熱食有甜品， 職員在這裏也非常 細心地留意每一位同學的需要會幫手斟橙汁斟水而且會 神速地收碟。 汽水橙汁是任飲的， 在暗角也提供熱檸水及咖啡機就是沒有人留意到就是了哭哭我要熱水, 第一次安排 師生出去拎嘢食嗰陣 就真係排長龍。。。technical方面， 不敢說全部 但是大部分的職員也懂得操作panel所以有什麼需要跟職員說明即可， 可以帶電腦播歌播片， 留意可能要帶返自己嘅adapter。 小小缺點就係 目測沒有 電梯 直達 會廳的那一層坐輪椅的朋友要親自跟酒店確認一下。
廁所係 宴會廳的出面， 女厠入面有兩格， 去廁所幾次都冇話要排長龍咁樣亦不用等但系…… 你懂的女人就是很愛扮靚。

Prima hotel op toplocatie in Hong Kong voor een redelijke prijs. Vriendelijk personeel. Bij het inchecken wordt wel meteen geprobeerd om de boeking te upgraden. We hebben dit gedaan, maar ik vraag me af of dit nou echt veel extra was. Uitgebreid ontbijt. 

Oja: Verwacht niet teveel van de het uitzicht, alles in Hong Kong zit dicht op elkaar ;).
Tempat nya mewah. Sangat bagus untuk bersantai dan melihat sunrise.   Terletak di samping china ferry terminal.   Dekat dekat kowloon park cukup jalan kaki bentar
